- The integer array parameter `arr` must not be null.
- The integer parameter `k` must be greater than or equal to 1.
- The integer result is the maximum sub-array sum in the modified array after repeating the array `k` times.
- The length of the sub-array can be 0, and its sum in that case is 0.
- The integer result must be returned modulo 10^9 + 7.